description: Police say the investigation is being treated as an "isolated incident".
title: Murder arrest over death of woman at flat
title_page: Murder arrest over death of woman at flat in Lowestoft - BBC News
maintext:
A man has been arrested on suspicion of murder following the death of a woman at a flat.
The woman, in her 40s, died at an address in London Road South, Lowestoft.
Suffolk Police were called by the ambulance service just after 07:10 GMT.
A 49-year-old man, from Lowestoft, is being questioned on suspicion of murder.
